00:09:24.623 --> 00:09:26.224
Thank you so much.

00:09:52.640 --> 00:09:53.641
Pin?

00:09:54.663 --> 00:09:55.664
Sanya.

00:09:56.400 --> 00:09:59.600
Have you seen Sasin and Saenkaew?

00:10:02.720 --> 00:10:04.520
