00:10:33.320 --> 00:10:36.160
Is something bothering you?

00:10:39.177 --> 00:10:42.240
Maybe it's just all in my head.

00:10:50.000 --> 00:10:53.240
Whatever it is bothering you,

00:10:53.440 --> 00:10:55.041
