00:14:17.023 --> 00:14:19.024
and understanding.

00:14:28.150 --> 00:14:29.151
Thank you.

00:14:56.080 --> 00:14:59.320
Where have you been? I didn't see you.

00:14:59.577 --> 00:15:01.280
