00:25:04.903 --> 00:25:05.904
Okay.

00:25:12.337 --> 00:25:13.400
Hey,

00:25:15.377 --> 00:25:16.880
hey!

00:25:20.400 --> 00:25:22.240
This is your document.

00:25:24.290 --> 00:25:26.091
- Thanks.
